  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602120/extras/746d3d0439008eb517753fa2f2a2add1.poster.avif?t=1747780749\" width=800 height=88 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602120/extras/746d3d0439008eb517753fa2f2a2add1.webm?t=1747780749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602120/extras/746d3d0439008eb517753fa2f2a2add1.mp4?t=1747780749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bob's Mansion is an immersive first-person horror game that takes you on a thrilling journey through the dark eerie remnants of your old family home. Take the role of Mike Jingle. A 22 year old guy, who one day receives a letter asking him to return to his family home. Now you return home to find your family missing. Use your Parkour skills to search the darkness and uncover the secrets that lurk within. Are you brave enough to face the unknown?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602120/extras/9f46cf7ea6ea3e14f674d09ec8d664be.poster.avif?t=1747780749\" width=800 height=88 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602120/extras/9f46cf7ea6ea3e14f674d09ec8d664be.webm?t=1747780749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602120/extras/9f46cf7ea6ea3e14f674d09ec8d664be.mp4?t=1747780749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Run, walk, climb</strong> and <strong>slide</strong> your way through the dark environment.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hide</strong> against unstoppable creatures.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight</strong> monstrous enemies with a unique prototype weapon.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive </strong>and explore the mansion and uncover the secrets beneath.  </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Random </strong>Item Placement and <strong>Permadeath</strong> mode.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Bob's Mansion is an chapter based horror game. The story is revealed via cutscenes, environmental storytelling and secret notes. Are you brave enough to face the <strong>Darkness Inside</strong>?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602120/extras/51f8e19dc5e858bed01b585de5aed542.poster.avif?t=1747780749\" width=308 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602120/extras/51f8e19dc5e858bed01b585de5aed542.webm?t=1747780749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602120/extras/51f8e19dc5e858bed01b585de5aed542.mp4?t=1747780749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602120/extras/746d3d0439008eb517753fa2f2a2add1.poster.avif?t=1747780749\" width=800 height=88 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602120/extras/746d3d0439008eb517753fa2f2a2add1.webm?t=1747780749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602120/extras/746d3d0439008eb517753fa2f2a2add1.mp4?t=1747780749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bob's Mansion is an immersive first-person horror game that takes you on a thrilling journey through the dark eerie remnants of your old family home. Take the role of Mike Jingle. A 22 year old guy, who one day receives a letter asking him to return to his family home. Now you return home to find your family missing. Use your Parkour skills to search the darkness and uncover the secrets that lurk within. Are you brave enough to face the unknown?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602120/extras/9f46cf7ea6ea3e14f674d09ec8d664be.poster.avif?t=1747780749\" width=800 height=88 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602120/extras/9f46cf7ea6ea3e14f674d09ec8d664be.webm?t=1747780749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602120/extras/9f46cf7ea6ea3e14f674d09ec8d664be.mp4?t=1747780749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Run, walk, climb</strong> and <strong>slide</strong> your way through the dark environment.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hide</strong> against unstoppable creatures.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight</strong> monstrous enemies with a unique prototype weapon.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive </strong>and explore the mansion and uncover the secrets beneath.  </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Random </strong>Item Placement and <strong>Permadeath</strong> mode.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Bob's Mansion is an chapter based horror game. The story is revealed via cutscenes, environmental storytelling and secret notes. Are you brave enough to face the <strong>Darkness Inside</strong>?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602120/extras/51f8e19dc5e858bed01b585de5aed542.poster.avif?t=1747780749\" width=308 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602120/extras/51f8e19dc5e858bed01b585de5aed542.webm?t=1747780749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602120/extras/51f8e19dc5e858bed01b585de5aed542.mp4?t=1747780749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
